<h2>@ViewData["Title"]</h2>
<h3>@ViewData["Message"]</h3>

<p>
    Welfare Danmark is a leading company in the industry of
    welfare technologies. The company offers tested and efficient virtual solutions for rehabilitation.
    Welfare Denmark won the Microsoft Global Innovation Award in 2013 with Virtual Training®.
    WD has developed solutions for the healthcare industry in a close and formalized cooperation
    with several municipalities in Denmark. These municipalities have contributed significantly to the
    development of Welfare Denmark’s technologies on a management and therapist levels. Such
    productive cooperation enabled WD to offer solutions that fit into daily healthcare operations
    and that efficiently contribute to resolve the growing number of challenges posed by the
    healthcare industry to a society.
</p>
